# BuildMind — Environment Configuration
# No API keys required for basic operation.
# BuildMind uses your IDE's model access (Antigravity, Cursor, etc.)
#
# Only fill these in if you want to test with direct API access
# (e.g., running BuildMind outside of an IDE environment):

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...   # Optional — only for standalone mode
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...          # Optional fallback

# ── BuildMind settings (optional overrides) ──────────────────────────────────
# BUILDMIND_DEFAULT_MODEL=claude-sonnet
# BUILDMIND_LOG_LEVEL=INFO
